/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` v5.2.0+\n714: - `k8s.io/klog/v2` v2.130.1+\n715: - `github.com/stretchr/testify` v1.9.0+ (Testing)\n716: \n717: ### Blocked By\n718: - None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n719: \n720: ### Blocks\n721: - AR-009 (Router HTTP 反向代理核心) - Router may integrate with PicoD for code execution\n722: - AR-011 (Router JWT 认证与签发) - JWT authentication integration\n723: - Production deployment with PicoD as code execution engine\n724: \n725: ### Notes\n726: - PicoD uses RS256 signing algorithm for JWT authentication\n727: - Public key is loaded from `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` environment variable\n728: - Default port: 8080\n729: - Default timeout: 60 seconds\n730: - Maximum request body size: 32 MiB\n731: - Workspace jail enforced through path sanitization\n732: - All /api/* endpoints require JWT authentication\n733: - /health endpoint is publicly accessible\n734: - File modes default to 0644, maximum 0777\n735: - Directory mode: 0755\n736: - Timeout exit code: 124\n737: - Server supports graceful shutdown\n738: - ReadHeaderTimeout: 10 seconds\n739: - Gin runs in ReleaseMode\n740: - Error messages do not expose sensitive information\n741: - Logging uses klog with appropriate severity levels\n\n(End of file - total 741 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/picod`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: M\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Create pkg/picod package structure\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod` directory\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/constants.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/config.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/errors.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/auth.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/execute.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/files.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/server.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/handlers.go` file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/picod/middleware.go` file","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7